.env.*
!.env.example
# esbuild output — regenerated by `npm run build:js` / `build:css` (Plan B).
# Cloudflare Pages builds dist/ on deploy; GitHub Pages will serve a
# committed copy until the migration finishes (drop the `!dist/` line then).
dist/
